snippet.title: Phantom Brave: The Hermuda Triangle Remastered - PS5 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on the heartfelt first adventure of Marona and her Phantom companion Ash in Phantom Brave: The Hermuda Triangle Remastered, coming digitally to PlayStation 5 on November 7, 2024! 

For more info, visit nisamerica.com/phantombrave-remastered

#PhantomBrave #PhantomBraveHD
